    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=tk3uewofpx]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tk3uewofpx]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=vbcz13wal7]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vbcz13wal7]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=nsthwdi0n9]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nsthwdi0n9]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=j3gh6j23zg]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=j3gh6j23zg]{color:#476ebd}</style>To allow RenderMan to control your geometry settings, these can be found in the RenderMan tab inside the <strong><span data-colorid=\"nsthwdi0n9\">RenderGeometrySettings</span></strong> LOP <br /><br />(RfH needs to be installed)<br /><br />Choose <strong><span data-colorid=\"vbcz13wal7\">Set or Create</span></strong> or <strong><span data-colorid=\"j3gh6j23zg\">Set if Exists</span></strong> to create or change an opinion on the geometry attribute or choose <strong><span data-colorid=\"tk3uewofpx\">Block</span></strong> to disable previous opinions on the attribute. &nbsp;&nbsp;All available parameters are listed but none are set by default.<br /><br />These are the same settings that can be found in the RenderMan spare parameter tab on object nodes.<br /><br /><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderGeometrySettings.jpg\" width=\"1800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640572/RenderGeometrySettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761660397285&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=639\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640572/RenderGeometrySettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761660397285&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"651\" data-width=\"1833\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634290511\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderGeometrySettings.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640572\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"6ad0aadc-d8fc-4e9c-a802-5cd502fe6a18\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640572/RenderGeometrySettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761660397285&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1833&amp;height=651 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640572/RenderGeometrySettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761660397285&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=639 1x\" /></span><p><br /></p>"
